No. 408,

Mise.

White v. United States. Francis J. Larkin for petitioner. Solicitor General Griswold, Assistant Attorney General Vinson, and Beatrice Rosenberg for the United States.

C. A. 1st Cir. Certiorari denied.

Mr. Justice Black and Mr. Justice Stewart are of the opinion that certiorari should be granted.
